instruction:
Please perform a targeted query within the company’s centralized human resources management system (HRMS) to retrieve comprehensive details about the employee named Zhang San, adhering to the following structured requirements:  
1. **Duplicate Handling**: If multiple active employees (as of the current query date, formatted as YYYY-MM-DD) share the exact full name "Zhang San", first generate a preliminary differentiation list containing each duplicate’s unique employee ID, job title, and primary work location to enable precise selection;  
2. **Core Employment Details**: For the specified employee (or each duplicate if differentiation is needed), provide:  
   a. The official onboarding date (formatted as YYYY-MM-DD) reflecting their first day of active service with the company;  
   b. The full, unabbreviated official name of their currently assigned department (excluding any internal aliases or shorthand);  
3. **Salary Breakdown**: Disclose the employee’s latest effective monthly salary components (valid for the current pay cycle), including:  
   a. Base salary (fixed monthly compensation per the signed employment contract);  
   b. Performance-based salary (variable component calculated based on the most recent completed quarterly performance appraisal score);  
   c. Fixed subsidies (itemized if applicable, covering housing allowance, transportation subsidy, meal allowance, and any other non-variable stipends);  
   d. Total after-tax monthly salary (net amount post-deduction of statutory social security contributions, individual income tax, and mandatory deductions per national laws and company policies).  

Ensure all data presented aligns with the latest HRMS entries and excludes any historical records marked as inactive or archived.
